data.title: Katy Perry Los Angeles Tickets
data.meta_description: Great tickets for the Katy Perry Los Angeles concerts  are on-sale now. Get 2024 Katy Perry Los Angeles Tickets today!
data.text:
Catch the Smile Tour Live in 2024!

Katy Perry is coming home to LA this summer, and she's giving her SoCal fans four chances to catch her live and in person! Tickets are available for all scheduled Katy Perry Los Angeles shows, which means you've got plenty of opportunities to hear her singing "Roar," "Never Really Over," "Dark Horse," and more, live and in person. Check out the schedule below to find out more, and get your set of Katy Perry Los Angeles Tickets now!
